2188300/extras/e79c3462d987fd28f6f8d055925d87f3.mp4?t=1669433654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。<br><br><br>砸碎任何妨碍你的噱头!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188300/extras/HookEscaper_BreakEnemy.gif ?t=1669433654\" /></span>.<br><br><br>你必须自己开辟道路!<br>即使是那些看起来阻碍你的东西也能帮助你！这就是所谓的 &quot;帮助&quot;。",
